<span id="freeTextContainer15325994564790422702">I was in mood for some Romance novel.. <br/>Not a feel good fluffy kind of romance which Kasie West writes. This time for some serious shit.<br/>Notable name <b>sparked</b> was Mr.Sparks...<br/><br/>Heard a lot about his novels and movies and uncertain about when and through which of his work I would get into his whirlwind. And it happened in the middle of Bent Road..<br/><br/>Yes, this is a love story with a tinge of mystery mixed in (if that is considered a mystery).<br/><br/>Though characters were bleak and non-attachable, story was not s</span>
  <span id="freeText15325994564790422702" style="display:none">I was in mood for some Romance novel.. <br />Not a feel good fluffy kind of romance which Kasie West writes. This time for some serious shit.<br />Notable name <b>sparked</b> was Mr.Sparks...<br /><br />Heard a lot about his novels and movies and uncertain about when and through which of his work I would get into his whirlwind. And it happened in the middle of Bent Road..<br /><br />Yes, this is a love story with a tinge of mystery mixed in (if that is considered a mystery).<br /><br />Though characters were bleak and non-attachable, story was not so bad.<br />Though you know what happens in next scene, you couldn't help to wonder how it happens and to which degree it escalates..<br /><br />Yaaaaaa... Get through your past and move on..<br />Except it's easier said than done..<br /><br />I donno.. <br />A decent start for me perhaps..</span>
